{"tid":2169199,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"9.1推全民檢測  林鄭認大海撈針 何栢良：浪費子彈","createTime":"2020-08-22T10:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T10:25:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a081c8ef76b13add429b1e1fc651d15d23540a23","tid":2169199,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:05:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/3PWERBITLVFUDHH66TOKG3S2FE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2F3PWERBITLVFUDHH66TOKG3S2FE%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6XdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=61d95235\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2F3PWERBITLVFUDHH66TOKG3S2FE%2F&h=6faf8c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/3PWERBITLVFUDHH66TOKG3S2FE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n9.1推全民檢測 <br />\n林鄭認大海撈針 何栢良：浪費子彈<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】從檢測機構到採樣方式均由中央主導的「普及社區檢測計劃」將於9月1日開始，免費為全民作自願性病毒檢測，為期14日。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良認為計劃缺乏針對性，是浪費子彈。特首林鄭月娥承認計劃是「大海撈針」，但「今次非常高興得到中央的支援」，決意推行。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：777拒向第三波68死者道歉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rrY1Ur06kXu8PmTFxRg0ZVh15Uo=/2564x1122/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JP5RA6X23NGARFOOO3R2EQOM5U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrrY1Ur06kXu8PmTFxRg0ZVh15Uo%3D%2F2564x1122%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJP5RA6X23NGARFOOO3R2EQOM5U.gif&h=ab3dc32a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■來自廣州的多名核酸檢測人員昨日抵港，周浩鼎、鄧家彪及陸俊雄等建制派到檢測人員下榻的酒店歡迎他們。央視網頁圖片<br />\n<br />\n據中共官媒《人民日報》報道，來自廣州的50名核酸檢測人員已於昨日中午。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n特區在整項計劃上任由中央擺佈，檢測機構也由中央欽點，林鄭則指出，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：基因重構面孔助監控<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5Yno1I183LTyIcMrGrOg4ck4EmY=/2130x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XWZTBNWG3BAF7NSSGCACTKQ2PA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5Yno1I183LTyIcMrGrOg4ck4EmY%3D%2F2130x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXWZTBNWG3BAF7NSSGCACTKQ2PA.jpg&h=e1489003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/B0-6t1lGRjjEdj9-eakTiYy2O5s=/2158x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EVQWUHUJSVB2JCPEPWYMAHKZ6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FB0-6t1lGRjjEdj9-eakTiYy2O5s%3D%2F2158x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEVQWUHUJSVB2JCPEPWYMAHKZ6U.jpg&h=9603a257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何栢良<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最多為期14日 可網上預約<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局長聶德權稱，計劃9月1日展開，首輪為期七日，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聶稱政府會物色較大室內場地作檢測中心，具有良好通風系統，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府抗疫顧問、中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌指出，全民檢測較理想是。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WyK2nrAAQ7jX34c_o5Po3Au8yPg=/1080x1224/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N3G2AWRT4JHJHGB5NCXXSJRLLI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWyK2nrAAQ7jX34c_o5Po3Au8yPg%3D%2F1080x1224%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN3G2AWRT4JHJHGB5NCXXSJRLLI.gif&h=d0e96917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n專家建議先檢測高風險人士<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良對檢測計劃的防疫成效有保留，他舉例說，近月北京、深圳能迅速控制疫情也非靠全民檢測，而是用早診斷早隔離的方法。他認為，應針對性做病毒檢測，否則浪費子彈。他建議為食肆、街市及超市的員工做檢測，成效比起為感染風險低的一般市民做檢測更大。<br />\n<br />\n感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷亦認為，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局昨向內部發信，邀請部門主管提名在職政府人員或退休公務員，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"bcd5e65c0c81155c551491e71983937485eb461d","tid":2169199,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"個阿姑喺狗面前拎刀隊人都有得保釋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2169225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2169225</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}